{"type":"message","id":"11437955","parentId":"7c9268ff","timestamp":"2026-03-20T02:20:48.807Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby asked about MY cron jobs. Let me filter for just finn's jobs:\n\n1. `fe9ff49a-df62-4f86-8958-d00f667442cd` - \"finances-update-reminder-1130pm\" - fires at 11:30pm tonight\n2. `eec1c29a-63ee-4b36-a6b9-0a202209ea11` - \"Finn Daily Bill Check\" - daily bill check\n\nBut I should also show him the others since they're all running on the system and might be relevant context. Actually he asked \"what cron jobs do YOU have\" so I'll focus on Finn jobs but mention the others briefly.\n\n\nI'm looking at my two scheduled jobs: a one-time reminder at 11:30pm tonight and a daily bill check that runs every 24 hours, though the system has five other jobs running for different agents.","thinkingSignature":"ce6329eea47c7a91e01b2e92692fe45abba2581ee1166126e6e5fb7dcdce9b85"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Just me (Finn):\n\n1. **finances-update-reminder-1130pm** — fires at 11:30pm tonight (one-shot, asks you to send updated finances)\n2. **Finn Daily Bill Check** — daily check for upcoming bills & financial alerts in Gmail\n\nThat's it for me! 🧊💸\n\nFor context, the whole crew's running:\n- **Emmy** — hourly email check + Pinterest unsubscribe reminder (11:30pm tonight)\n- **X** — daily 9:30am X cleanup reminder\n- **Morning Brief** — daily 5:30am via Dean"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":14065,"output":327,"cacheRead":19029,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33421,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773973231456}}
