{"type":"message","id":"8f23c7d3","parentId":"85af98bd","timestamp":"2026-03-20T02:25:20.032Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"He means the bills_tracker file he sent earlier. He wants me to use that file directly instead of Gmail. I should check that file and update my daily bill check cron job to read from the local file instead of checking Gmail.","thinkingSignature":"b13108ffbeac5c107cc3b9fd6e051b4dffb7cd8374c2d37e9b37fe564dc25b5a"},{"type":"text","text":"Oh! The bills tracker file you sent me — `/Desktop/SecondBrain/Finances/bills_tracker.md`. Got it. \n\nSo I should just read that file for your bill info instead of scraping emails. Makes sense — cleaner and more reliable. 👍\n\nWant me to update the daily bill check to point to that file now, or wait until you send me the updated version?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92,"output":128,"cacheRead":33523,"cacheWrite":568,"totalTokens":34311,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773973515021}}
