{"type":"message","id":"d12c283c","parentId":"eb7fcc33","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:03:26.596Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"44\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-20 01:03 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nI have 232$ cash in the bank. It’s rough out here."}],"timestamp":1773983006594}}
{"type":"message","id":"fd8ca7f9","parentId":"d12c283c","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:03:35.889Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby just told me he has $232 cash in the bank. That's pretty low. This is concerning but also I should be supportive. I shouldn't be preachy or make him feel bad. He shared this with me so I should acknowledge it and maybe gently connect it to why I'm here - to help him manage his bills and finances.\n\nI shouldn't immediately jump into \"let's set up reminders\" or be too proactive since he told me to hold off. But I can acknowledge the situation and let him know I'm here when he's ready.","thinkingSignature":"be976214142406bdf13b2fc94c0204eec016b5d6266dcf10880527c57646ea37"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] That's tough, fam. 😔\n\nI know — bills are piling up and the bank account is thin. It's stressful.\n\nI'm here whenever you want to figure out a game plan. Whether it's prioritizing which bills to tackle first, finding ways to cut costs, or just tracking what needs to get paid. \n\nMy job is to help you stay on top of this stuff so it doesn't spiral. Just say when. 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92,"output":203,"cacheRead":9670,"cacheWrite":24869,"totalTokens":34834,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773983006595}}
{"type":"message","id":"409ecd42","parentId":"fd8ca7f9","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:04:12.669Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"46\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-20 01:04 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nI give it to God. The father son and Holy Spirit got me"}],"timestamp":1773983052666}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1041430","parentId":"409ecd42","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:04:17.562Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is expressing faith - he trusts God with his finances. This is a personal moment. I should be respectful and supportive, not jump into \"fix it\" mode. Just meet him where he is.","thinkingSignature":"e1b1e398be016571fe5eccc8de0efdd42f43d83da5026bd9882e2a8c181b551f"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Respect. 🙏 \n\nThat's the way to be. Hard to stress about money when you've already handed it off. \n\nI'm still here when you need me — whether that's tomorrow, next week, or when the updated finances come through. My job doesn't go anywhere. 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92,"output":107,"cacheRead":34459,"cacheWrite":299,"totalTokens":34957,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773983052668}}
