{"type":"message","id":"815b011e","parentId":"27ac3e3e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T19:08:10.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hmm, I notice that the `finances-full-reminder-4pm` job (id: d3e81f0c) I set up earlier is no longer in the list. It looks like it may have been the one that I manually triggered earlier and it fired successfully. Wait, but I also manually triggered it and Bobby got it. So it fired and then was deleted (since it was a one-shot with deleteAfterRun).\n\nBut now it's gone from the list. The 4pm one should still be coming... wait, 4pm = 20:00 UTC = 2026-03-21T20:00:00Z. \n\nLet me verify - the manual trigger I did earlier was for the 4pm reminder itself, not the 8am one. That job should still be scheduled. I don't see it in the active list though, which is concerning. The job might have already fired and been removed, or perhaps I was mistaken about whether it was still there.\n\nLooking at the timestamps, it's currently 3:07pm EDT and the job was supposed to fire at 4pm - it should definitely still be active. I can't find the `finances-full-reminder-4pm` job anywhere in the current list. The only remaining reminders are the 8am one for tomorrow and the X cleanup ones. This is strange since the job was created successfully and I manually triggered it earlier, which should've worked based on what Bobby confirmed.\n\nWait - I think I see what happened. When I manually triggered it at 1:07pm, that was actually the 4pm job firing early because it was already due. So it ran successfully and then deleted itself as a one-shot job. That means Bobby got the test message he was supposed to get, but now the actual 4pm reminder doesn't exist anymore since it already fired and was removed. There's no pending 4pm job in the queue - it already fired when I tested it manually. If Bobby wants another reminder at 4pm, I'll need to schedule a new one.","thinkingSignature":"015b5c7e2f9dfd62d9a2aa3ee709c35d4c83bf45c3fcce57851c54fdbfb79ec7"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Bobby — that 4pm job is actually **gone**. I just checked and the one I set up earlier already fired (it was the one I manually triggered at 1:07pm as a test, and since it was a one-shot, it deleted itself after firing).\n\nSo that test you confirmed? That WAS the 4pm reminder — it just fired early by accident when I triggered it.\n\nWant me to set up another 4pm reminder? I can do it now. 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":27590,"output":534,"cacheRead":19030,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47154,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774120074825}}
