{"type":"message","id":"4a6a76ac","parentId":"fb51b085","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:42:58.460Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the logs, I can see around 21:57 there was a Telegram timeout issue. But I don't see a clear entry for the finances-tonight-10pm job firing or failing.\n\nWait - the job `finances-tonight-10pm` was set to fire at `2026-03-22T02:00:00Z` (10pm ET). But the current time is `Fri 2026-03-21 23:42 EDT` which is `2026-03-22 03:42:00Z`. So the job should have fired about 1 hour 42 minutes ago.\n\nBut the job is no longer in the list (deleted after run). Yet Bobby didn't receive a message. \n\nSo it fired and got deleted, but the message never reached Bobby. Let me trace the cron job execution around that timestamp to see what happened.","thinkingSignature":"8d5b2ba2f11842098be745606eb1a23db718099cb872b37dd5cc619f1d605fcb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xnegsv25ni44_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep \"7ebeb660\\|finances-tonight\" /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/logs/gateway.log | tail -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38397,"output":236,"cacheRead":20228,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58861,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774150970396}}
