{"type":"message","id":"b52cd05e","parentId":"0b44f62b","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:43:21.328Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sent directly. Now I should note that the 3pm tomorrow reminder is still set as a backup.","thinkingSignature":"82dc18205950dc06fa0a3d08c1e8278a0cdfc2f1ca8235ecb9405548c3dabedf"},{"type":"text","text":"\nSent! ✅ \n\nAnd the **3pm tomorrow** one is still armed as backup. You also still have the **8am tomorrow** one from the earlier setup. \n\nSorry for the miss — I'll get this sorted. Go finish your laundry! 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39542,"output":80,"cacheRead":20228,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59850,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774150996598}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f58716d","parentId":"b52cd05e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:46:06.901Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"82\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 23:46 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nno like you should have done it automatically without me messagiing you. how can you nudge me like i want you to every so often. give me options."}],"timestamp":1774151166896}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b3cad86","parentId":"2f58716d","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:46:16.500Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants a passive/background nudge system - something that fires automatically on a schedule without him having to message me first. He wants options for how often to be nudged about the finances.\n\nLet me think about what options to offer:\n1. Every hour - too aggressive\n2. Every 3 hours - pretty frequent\n3. Every 6 hours - moderate\n4. Twice daily (morning + evening) - reasonable\n5. Once a day - less aggressive\n6. Every 12 hours - moderate\n\nHe's been putting it off for a while so maybe something that's not too annoying but persistent enough to get it done. I should offer him a few schedule options and let him pick.","thinkingSignature":"6a1da0ab4af3ea8fb729177d5e4cf4343834acadb2beaea2b76c4cd28140be8d"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Got it — you want me to auto-nudge you on a schedule without you having to ask. Here are some options:\n\n1. **Every 4 hours** — persistent but not insane\n2. **Every 8 hours** — twice a day, morning + night\n3. **Every 12 hours** — morning + evening\n4. **Once a day** — just one ping per day\n\nWhich one sounds right to you?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92,"output":239,"cacheRead":20228,"cacheWrite":38706,"totalTokens":59265,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774151166900}}
