{"type":"message","id":"b53bf0c0","parentId":"73c27480","timestamp":"2026-04-03T04:21:17.558Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants me to create a file to track his earnings. He also wants to confirm what the goal was on April 1st.\n\nLooking back at the conversation:\n- On April 1st, Bobby's goal was $125/day net (after gas). He started at 4:30pm and made $119.13.\n- He then changed it to $147/day gross on April 2nd (which is $125 net after gas - so the net goal stayed the same, just the gross changed since he was accounting for gas differently now)\n\nActually wait, let me re-read. On March 31, Bobby said his goal every day is $125 AFTER gas (net 125). \n\nThen on April 1, Dean messaged saying \"Bobby's goal tomorrow: $125 on DoorDash\" and set up the 9am and 2pm nudges.\n\nThen on April 1 night/early April 2, Bobby said the goal is $125 net and $147 gross.\n\nSo on April 1, the goal was $125 (the net goal). He made $119.13.\n\nThen on April 2, he updated it to $147 gross / $125 net going forward.\n\nFor the carryover calculation on April 2: $152.87 = $147 (new daily gross) + $5.87 (carryover from April 1 when he made $119.13 vs $125 goal)\n\nSo yes, April 1 goal was $125.\n","thinkingSignature":"93b074e02713ef767bf0002062da8ad0cb1a791524caf8fcc2dab9d5ddcd4791"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s7kanc1t303d_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Bobby's DoorDash Earnings Tracker\n\n## Daily Earnings Log\n\n| Date | Earnings | Goal | Surplus/Deficit | Notes |\n|------|----------|------|-----------------|-------|\n| April 1 | $119.13 | $125.00 | -$5.87 | Started ~4:30pm, traffic cut it short |\n| April 2 | $159.91 | $147.00 | +$12.91 | CRUSHED IT! Big orders, $5.87 carryover from Apr 1 |\n\n## Running Totals\n\n- **Total earned (Apr 1-2):** $279.04\n- **Total goal (Apr 1-2):** $272.00\n- **Overall surplus:** +$7.04\n\n---\n\n*Last updated: 2026-04-03*","filePath":"/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/SecondBrain/Fina