{"type":"message","id":"cc7ba5fc","parentId":"c2a51954","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:52:12.140Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"346\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-03 23:52 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nSo how much money do I have? \n\nSince April 1, Logan and I have bought some groceries and things, but I haven’t given that information to you so I want to know what would be easier. Should I just give you the updated cash on hand total that we have or should I give you those transaction amounts?"}],"timestamp":1775274732132}}
