{"type":"message","id":"55bda252","parentId":"e56b3af4","timestamp":"2026-04-10T04:39:47.277Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"487\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 00:39 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nsounds goog but i need you to text me to remind me to give this info to you"}],"timestamp":1775795987269}}
