{"type":"message","id":"4a9de248","parentId":"380dcd70","timestamp":"2026-04-10T04:42:22.467Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is stressed. He just shared something vulnerable. I should acknowledge that, be supportive, and reassure him.","thinkingSignature":"2f74d81b46381668091a26e9743fc891eb010632c2ee7f4bce822bad1bcdde46"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] I hear you Bobby. Money stress is real — especially when you're trying to make a big move and everything feels like it's adding up.\n\nBut here's what I want you to hear:\n\nYou're DOING the work. You're grinding DD every day. You're tracking. You're paying bills on time. You're having hard conversations with yourself about goals.\n\nThat's more than most people do.\n\nTomorrow is a new day. One day at a time. You don't have to figure out May and June right now — just tomorrow.\n\nGo get some sleep. I'll be here in the morning and we'll start fresh. You've got this. 💪🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98,"output":158,"cacheRead":143769,"cacheWrite":242,"totalTokens":144267,"cost":{"input":0.0000294,"output":0.0001896,"cacheRead":0.00862614,"cacheWrite":0.00009075,"total":0.00893589}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775796134982,"responseId":"0627b2a7ed318667fd91f7829df8a6b4"}}
