{"type":"message","id":"28d7d250","parentId":"18a1ab0b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T22:01:10.617Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"544\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 18:01 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nYes and I do have bonds I can cash. Okay good. I’ll give you all transactions! Help me keep up!"}],"timestamp":1775858470613}}
{"type":"message","id":"62bef63f","parentId":"28d7d250","timestamp":"2026-04-10T22:01:15.832Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is committed to tracking everything and working the plan. Let me give him a final send-off to enjoy his hockey game and get ready for a big push.","thinkingSignature":"df53aae0d3a4ffb3e5d49764ee05b5f43fbd675fad2314b3a89c14c9baa2caef"},{"type":"text","text":"That's the spirit! Every transaction, every dollar — we track it together.\n\nGo enjoy your hockey game tonight, then get out there and stack what you can. Tomorrow is a new day, $164 goal.\n\nI'm here. Every step of the way. Let's get you to NY. 💪🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98,"output":100,"cacheRead":151935,"cacheWrite":370,"totalTokens":152503,"cost":{"input":0.0000294,"output":0.00011999999999999999,"cacheRead":0.009116099999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00013875,"total":0.009404249999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775858470618,"responseId":"0628a6265ecb6cf343cc523841ed85b1"}}
