{"type":"message","id":"5e444f7b","parentId":"3b5d9949","timestamp":"2026-04-10T22:02:45.754Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"548\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 18:02 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nAnd is that 125 net? Or 125 total goal?"}],"timestamp":1775858565749}}
{"type":"message","id":"00712f99","parentId":"5e444f7b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T22:02:54.514Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby's asking about whether the $125 is net (after gas) or gross (before gas). From our earlier conversations:-$147 was the gross DD goal (before gas)\n- $125 was the net goal (after the $22 gas allotment)Let me clarify this for him.","thinkingSignature":"2e68e05ecea3ea20522b2fabd8ad1f27df974df858026f4cc58111686487c94f"},{"type":"text","text":"$125 was your **net goal** (after gas).\n\n**Original setup:**\n- Gross DD goal: $147/day\n- Gas: -$22/day\n- Net goal: $125/day\n\nSo the calendar at $125/day is assuming you're netting $125 after gas.\n\nWhen we talk about $164/day now — that's the GROSS number you'd need to earn to cover:\n- $125 net\n- + get ahead on the gap\n\nSo yes — $125 net is what hits your pocket after the $22 gas comes out. $164 gross is what you need to earn BEFORE gas to get ahead.\n\nDoes that make sense? 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98,"output":197,"cacheRead":152410,"cacheWrite":412,"totalTokens":153117,"cost":{"input":0.0000294,"output":0.0002364,"cacheRead":0.0091446,"cacheWrite":0.00015450000000000001,"total":0.0095649}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775858565754,"responseId":"0628a68661516117bf6ff434aed6618d"}}
