{"type":"message","id":"2d09dcaa","parentId":"4277a39d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T22:09:40.709Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby paid the $196.59 T-Mobile bill from his Y12. So his Y12 balance would decrease.\n\nBefore: $273.14 (before he told me at 5:57pm)\nAfter paying $196.59: $273.14 - $196.59 = $76.55\n\nWait, but I also had his Y12 at $273.14 at 5:57pm. Now he says he paid it from Y12, so his Y12 should be:\n$273.14 - $196.59 = $76.55\n\nLet me update the cash totals:\n- Bobby DD: $241.72 (same)\n- Bobby Y12: $273.14 - $196.59 = $76.55\n\n\n- Logan: $914.44 (same, paid Valvoline from his own funds)\n\nThat brings the new total to $1,232.71. His T-Mobile bill is now marked as paid.","thinkingSignature":"4a999da2e3c83f0ed771bd22718537de40fd8d8c1254bda6752b1d00f4610d4b"},{"type":"text","text":"Got it!\n\n**Y12 before:** $273.14\n**T-Mobile paid:** -$196.59\n**Y12 after:** $76.55\n\n**Updated cash totals:**\n- Bobby DD: $241.72\n- Bobby Y12: $76.55\n- Logan: $914.44\n- **New total: $1,232.71**\n\nLet me update the tracker:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fang7yozvo0h_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/SecondBrain/Finances/April_Bills.md","edits":[{"newText":"| April 10 | T-Mobile (phone bill) | $196.59 | ✅ PAID Apr 10 |","oldText":"| April 10 | T-Mobile (phone bill) | $196.59 | ⚠️ UNPAID - what is this? |"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98,"output":396,"cacheRead":153189,"cacheWrite":220,"totalTokens":153903,"cost":{"input":0.0000294,"output":0.0004752,"cacheRead":0.00919134,"cacheWrite":0.0000825,"total":0.00977844}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775858970871,"responseId":"0628a81b72757bf4728595bd0cdf11e4"}}
