{"type":"message","id":"bedc89f0","parentId":"5edbd7c9","timestamp":"2026-04-18T08:48:55.164Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n  \"message_id\": \"711\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-18 04:48 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nWell for yesterday I made 89.90 on DD and Logan and I also started working for Amazon flex we made 87 on the route we took so if I make the remaining of the 200 this morning today. Make sense?"}],"timestamp":1776502135155}}
{"type":"message","id":"d141df00","parentId":"bedc89f0","timestamp":"2026-04-18T08:49:07.581Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay so let me understand:\n\nYesterday (April 17):\n- DD: $89.90\n- Amazon Flex: $87 (Logan + Bobby together)\n- Total: $176.90\n\nToday (April 18 morning):\n- He needs $23.10 more to hit $200 for the combined work\n\nSo $89.90 + $87 + $23.10 = $200 total\n\nBut wait - is the Amazon Flex money separate from DD or combined? It sounds like Logan and Bobby worked a route together for Amazon Flex. The $87 was from that route, not from DD.\n\nSo the $200 goal might be their COMBINED goal for the day (DD + Amazon Flex) or just DD?\n\nI think Bobby is saying the $200 goal is for the combined work (DD + Amazon Flex). They made $89.90 on DD + $87 on Amazon Flex = $176.90. If he makes $23.10 more today, that hits $200 for the day.\n\nThat makes sense! I'll roll with it.","thinkingSignature":"fe083d50314f8257a41c3a90710adbfe99c31689fbbc921a04428158922a0e1a"},{"type":"text","text":"Yes it makes total sense! \n\n**April 17 combined:**\n- DD: $89.90\n- Amazon Flex (Logan + you): $87\n- **Total: $176.90**\n\nIf you make $23.10 this morning, you'd hit **$200 combined** for the day!\n\nThat's creative — Amazon Flex on top of DD! Smart diversification Bobby. Keep me posted on what you make this morning! 💪🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98,"output":313,"cacheRead":173840,"cacheWrite":372,"totalTokens":174623,"cost":{"input":0.0000294,"output":0.00037559999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0104304,"cacheWrite":0.0001395,"total":0.0109749}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776502135164,"responseId":"063278771e3be0815e8a210bdbf25a93"}}
