{"type":"message","id":"7fb281cb","parentId":"2c23608a","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.014Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby's saying the bills tracker is outdated and he doesn't want me to worry about the overdue bills being current. He's just using this as a reference to give me context on his bills, similar to what he's shared with Dean. He's not worried about it right now.\n\nI should acknowledge this and confirm I've got the context now. I should save this to my workspace for reference.","thinkingSignature":"52824bec7482289e00c555aff22a613a6172dac8a1cd73bf1811b91db502c272"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Ha, fair enough! No fretting. 😅\n\nSo you've got a whole bill ecosystem:\n- Xfinity, KUB, T-Mobile (utilities)\n- Capital One Platinum, Capital One Quicksilver, Discover, Chase (cards)\n- Geico (insurance)\n- Affirm for various purchases (Hilton, T-Mobile, BroadwayDirect)\n- Apple One, Flex (rent)\n\nGot it — I'll store this away and set up some reminders to hit you up before stuff comes due. 👍"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92,"output":185,"cacheRead":25055,"cacheWrite":2194,"totalTokens":27526,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773970718682}}
