{"type":"message","id":"8ff9b22b","parentId":"ed37d5d3","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.014Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants me to remind him to give me updated finances soon. He said don't set up reminders yet, but just shoot him a text. I should send him a message now asking about his finances, or at least acknowledging the request. Actually, re-reading - he said \"remind me to give you my updated finances soon. Just shoot me a text.\" - I think he wants me to remember to ask him about it later. \n\nWait - \"Just shoot me a text\" - maybe he wants me to just message him now to remind him? But that doesn't make sense since we're already texting.\n\nI think he means: in a few days, reach out and ask him for the updated finances. \n\nSo I should save this to memory and set a cron job to follow up with him in a couple days.","thinkingSignature":"ae0e2433e5ea2b82cd23dce18e3240b0b483b81243f34ec15813c90cea301f4d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nif33ptp87ap_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 2026-03-19\n\n## Session Start\n- First contact with Bobby via Telegram\n- Introduced myself: Finn 🧊💸, finance & bills assistant\n- Met the fam: Dean (general), Emmy (email), X (Twitter)\n- Emoji chosen: 🧊💸\n\n## Bill Tracker\n- Bobby shared his bill tracker from SecondBrain/Finances\n- Don't set up reminders yet\n- **TODO:** Bobby will provide updated finances soon — remind him to share\n  - He handles: Xfinity, KUB, T-Mobile, Capital One, Discover, Chase, Geico, Affirm, Apple One, Flex\n  - Said it's a bit outdated (OVERDUE items from March 4/9 are handled)\n  - Next step: wait for him to send updated tracker\n\n## Notes\n- Bobby said not to worry about the overdue bills\n- Just saving context for now, will act when he sends updates\n","file_path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-finn/memory/2026-03-19.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":