{"type":"message","id":"a09fc921","parentId":"9a2f97a4","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.016Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is expressing faith - he trusts God with his finances. This is a personal moment. I should be respectful and supportive, not jump into \"fix it\" mode. Just meet him where he is.","thinkingSignature":"e1b1e398be016571fe5eccc8de0efdd42f43d83da5026bd9882e2a8c181b551f"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Respect. 🙏 \n\nThat's the way to be. Hard to stress about money when you've already handed it off. \n\nI'm still here when you need me — whether that's tomorrow, next week, or when the updated finances come through. My job doesn't go anywhere. 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92,"output":107,"cacheRead":34459,"cacheWrite":299,"totalTokens":34957,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773983052668}}
