{"type":"message","id":"9f7cbe7c","parentId":"a5ab2d17","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.024Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"From what I can see on Bobby's Desktop, the files/folders I use are:\n\n1. **SecondBrain/** - This is where the bills_tracker.md lives that Bobby shared with me. Inside SecondBrain/Finances/ is the bills tracker.\n2. **money-tracker/** - This is a folder on the Desktop that might be related to my work.\n\nThe rest (Recipes, RexResearch, RexVideos, Find My, Google Chrome, Messages, Music, TV, Telegram, Mission Control.app, alex_finn_openclaw_summary.md, apartment_link.md, mission-control-*.json) are either Dean-related or other agents' stuff.\n\n\nSo for Finn specifically, I really only need the bills_tracker file from SecondBrain and the money-tracker folder to do my work.","thinkingSignature":"2d98e9612d590587d4521433940f610962e5d4e5f8216b18bf0542379baa7195"},{"type":"text","text":"**Finn's Desktop files:**\n\n1. **SecondBrain/Finances/bills_tracker.md** — the bill tracker you gave me (lives inside SecondBrain)\n2. **money-tracker/** — folder I may reference for your finances\n\nEverything else on your Desktop is for Dean, X, Rex, or other stuff. You can safely clean the rest.\n\nWhat specifically did Bobby want to clean up? I can help him figure out what to keep vs toss. 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":22457,"output":260,"cacheRead":18170,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40887,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774842140788,"responseId":"0619241c0ac1c378d43f7e2225dee233"}}
