{"type":"message","id":"eb96fc1e","parentId":"fd3f5ade","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.029Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is asking for his bills total for this week (ending Saturday). Let me look at the April Bills file and figure out which ones are due between now and Saturday (April 4, 2026).\n\nToday is April 1, 2026 (Wednesday). Saturday is April 4, 2026.\n\nFrom the April Bills:\n- April 1: Xfinity Internet - $118.00 (TODAY)\n- April 2: Affirm - Marriott Hotels - $129.59\n- April 3: KUB (old apartment) - $362.20 (flagged as not urgent)\n- April 8: T-Mobile (2 of 2) - $98.30\n\nSo bills due by Saturday April 4:\n- April 1 (today): $118.00\n- April 2: $129.59\n- April 3: $362.20 (KUB - not urgent, old apartment)\n\nThat's $118 + $129.59 + $362.20 = $609.79 by Saturday.\n\nIf he's asking about bills due this week specifically (not including the KUB since it's not urgent/old address), it would be $118 + $129.59 = $247.59.\n\nI'll give him both numbers since one of those bills isn't really his problem anymore.","thinkingSignature":"cf1d97c3843f8670c52865de0ede022f9030d64fa6cf99ffd645b52f46357472"},{"type":"text","text":"Here's what's due by Saturday (April 4):\n\n**Bills hitting this week:**\n- April 1 (today): Xfinity — $118.00\n- April 2: Affirm - Marriott Hotels — $129.59\n- April 3: KUB (old apartment) — $362.20 ⚠️\n\n**Total: $609.79**\n\nBut that KUB one is flagged as not urgent since you're not there anymore — that one's kinda separate.\n\n**Actual pressing bills: $247.59**\n\nGood luck out there tonight Bobby! Go stack 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":86,"output":395,"cacheRead":81767,"cacheWrite":192,"totalTokens":82440,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775074960442,"responseId":"061cb1908392b4787415297a2966f886"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c0063e6c","parentId":"eb96fc1e","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.029Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"209\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-01 16:26 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nSo if I make 125 from today till Saturday the 4th, how much would I have made?"}],"timestamp":1775075177695}}
