{"type":"message","id":"cdb6e082","parentId":"1df71d4e","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.030Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is stuck in traffic on the interstate and can't get out. He's already hit $119.13 which is $5.87 short of his $125 goal. He's been stuck for 30 minutes. He could try to keep going but sitting in traffic isn't worth $5.\n\nI should validate his decision. He's had a great night already - $119 in about 4 hours (started around 4:30, it's now 9:35 so about 5 hours). That's $23+/hour which is great.\n\n$119/125 = 95% - he basically hit his goal. Sitting in traffic for potentially another 30-60 minutes for $5 isn't worth it. \n\nSometimes you just have to call it a win and head home.","thinkingSignature":"2780d5a0493bc72246b08b545a2c796b1c3803c507a6b842323c4bbb404c7779"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Hey — that's NOT bad news. That's just the universe saying \"you did enough, Bobby.\"\n\n$119 in about 5 hours of work. You hit 95% of your goal and you're exhausted in traffic. That $5 you'd \"earn\" sitting in 30+ more minutes of gridlock? Not worth your time, your sanity, or your gas.\n\nGo home. Celebrate the win. You earned $119 tonight and you don't have to prove anything else tonight.\n\nTomorrow's a new day. 💪🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":86,"output":269,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":84364,"totalTokens":84719,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775093703376,"responseId":"061cfac8af2ce821c28bd77aec588327"}}
