{"type":"message","id":"4cab275e","parentId":"91e2af0b","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.034Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is seeing an approval request that came through. This looks like an Emmy email check thing trying to run. Let me explain briefly - this is an approval request for an elevated command. I don't have context about this specific request but I should tell Bobby what it is and let him know to approve/deny if needed.\n","thinkingSignature":"7a32867a63c0d1dd3470ed1bac5c7c6a4e572eae3e452871503009429f338be0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThat's an approval request — looks like Emmy tried to run a Gmail check (email-related script) and needs permission to access your Gmail. It's a security safeguard so no agent can just run random commands on your system without you knowing.\n\nIf you trust Emmy to check your emails, you can approve it. Otherwise you can deny it.\n\nWant me to ask Dean/Emmy about it, or do you want to just approve/deny it yourself? 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":582,"output":163,"cacheRead":97024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97769,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775258551991,"responseId":"061f7eb80deab03a33b4dbb8b2a3005b"}}
