{"type":"message","id":"7e0a527a","parentId":"a19a9b66","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.041Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is saying that his car is more important right now - he needs to get new brake pads and put them on the car before paying bills. This makes sense as safety is priority. So he needs to figure out how much brake pads cost and that's coming out of his $1,016.33 before bills. I should just acknowledge and support this decision - car safety comes first.\n","thinkingSignature":"64350e562cc6f413a0e8b02451bccec2b9979bf934ad2b92cce94e8442917861"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n100% — car safety first. Brake pads are more important than bills right now. \n\nHow much are the brake pads gonna cost you? That'll tell us what you're working with before we start paying bills. 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":379,"output":127,"cacheRead":110848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111354,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775318680308,"responseId":"062069996c46f9af8a0865bb1bd4953d"}}
