{"type":"message","id":"1b772d6e","parentId":"02e1d7fe","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.047Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me track this:\n\nYesterday (Apr 7): $123.61 + $15 reimbursement = $138.61 actual\nShort of $147 = $147 - $138.61 = $8.39 short\n\nToday (Apr 8): $120.40\nShort of $148.20 = $148.20 - $120.40 = $27.80 short\n\nTotal short over the 2 days = $8.39 + $27.80 = $36.19\n\nOver the next 7 days (Apr 9-15):\n$36.19 ÷ 7 = ~$5.17 extra per day\n\nNew goal = $148.20 + $5.17 = ~$153.37/day\n\n\nRounding to the nearest dollar, that puts us at $153/day for the next week.","thinkingSignature":"6520225aa740fa115525d8538ed717039f9b1b1f8ff02d13c796514795942289"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**Shortfall breakdown:**\n- Apr 7: $8.39 short (from $147)\n- Apr 8: $27.80 short (from $148.20)\n\n**Total: $36.19 to make up**\n\n**$36.19 ÷ 7 days = $5.17 extra per day**\n\n**New goal Apr 9-15: ~$153/day**\n\nThat's a $153 daily goal for the next 7 days to get back to even. 💪🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":121691,"output":279,"cacheRead":544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122514,"cost":{"input":0.0365073,"output":0.0003348,"cacheRead":0.00003264,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03687474}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775701194060,"responseId":"06263fca8f11307970d4c6fd909a058a"}}
