{"type":"message","id":"0c03bd74","parentId":"490399fc","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.048Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me calculate:\n\n- Bobby DD card: $259.01\n- Bobby Y12 (app shows): $416.22 but adjusted for Citizens Pay ($149.04) and gas ($22)\n- Actual Y12 estimate: $416.22 - $149.04 + $22? Wait no, the Y12 shows the current balance, and the transactions happen later. So the $416.22 is BEFORE those transactions cleared. \n\nActually re-reading: \"on my app it says i have 416.22 in my y12 but i know i paid 149.04 for my citizens pay (remind me tomorrow to give you more info about that) and i know i spent 22 on gas today so y12 will have to be a rough estimate for now until it updates\"\n\n\nSo the Y12 balance is probably already reduced by those transactions since they happened today, or they might still be pending. Given the timing, I'm estimating around $394 as a working figure for now until Bobby can verify the actual amount.","thinkingSignature":"f0e3fab3a4df522dc2cdc65fa0032838265cfe74aff5d8004a1888bcb16cead1"},{"type":"text","text":"Frustrating when bills show up days later! � frustration\n\nRough estimate:\n- Bobby DD: $259.01\n- Bobby Y12: ~$394.18 (app shows $416.22 but Citizens Pay + gas probably haven't cleared yet)\n- Logan Y12: $1,030.19\n\n**Rough total: ~$1,683.38**\n\nWe can nail it down tomorrow when everything updates. Citizens Pay sounds like a new bill — remind me and we'll categorize it! 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":80,"output":319,"cacheRead":92542,"cacheWrite":161,"totalTokens":93102,"cost":{"input":0.000024,"output":0.0003828,"cacheRead":0.005552519999999999,"cacheWrite":0.000060375000000000004,"total":0.0060196949999999985}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775706570588,"responseId":"062654cb6165ea6d2811e9f10aaa8d49"}}
