{"type":"message","id":"1202fdc4","parentId":"49a522d5","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.050Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby ended with $152.20 against a $162 goal. So he was $9.80 short for today.\n\nRunning tally of shortfalls:\n- Apr 7: $8.39 short\n- Apr 8: $27.80 short\n- Apr 9: $9.80 short\n\nTotal shortfall: $8.39 + $27.80 + $9.80 = $45.99\n\nNow he has 21 days left (Apr 10-30): $45.99 ÷ 21 = ~$2.19 extra per day needed\n\nNew goal: $162 + $2.19 = ~$164.19/day for remaining 21 days","thinkingSignature":"23fcab652e9de0f1a528200e28d6c9d90e3c467d2571c2341726b20ebf32e790"},{"type":"text","text":"**$152.20 — $9.80 short of $162**\n\nRunning shortfall total:\n- Apr 7: $8.39\n- Apr 8: $27.80\n- Apr 9: $9.80\n\n**Total: $45.99 to make up**\n\n**21 days left (Apr 10-30): $45.99 ÷ 21 = $2.19 extra/day**\n\n**New adjusted goal: ~$164/day for remaining 21 days**\n\nStill doable! $164/day and you're back on track by Apr 30! 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98,"output":267,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":131035,"totalTokens":131400,"cost":{"input":0.0000294,"output":0.0003204,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.049138125,"total":0.049487924999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775788824228,"responseId":"062796197a416093f6ad3cf547d7997b"}}
