{"type":"message","id":"d7b83970","parentId":"1fdc9f2e","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.051Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"447\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-09 22:43 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nUghhhhh okay well I’m going to a hockey game tomorrow and I won’t be able to DoorDash like I want and I also have to get my oil changed. \n\nI guess I will just let you know how much I make tomorrow and we will have to play it by ear"}],"timestamp":1775788996762}}
