{"type":"message","id":"baf0867d","parentId":"2f566d3f","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.057Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. The recurring 11pm daily reminder is set. Now Bobby will get a nightly nudge at 11pm every day to report his DD earnings and spending.","thinkingSignature":"848dcbb7088e2c8e9e1e6778aad128bbcf94be3751bc4e6a30d4325bc5fb3b22"},{"type":"text","text":"Done! **Every night at 11pm** I'll text you asking for:\n- DD earnings for the day\n- Any spending you had\n\nAnd I'll keep your gap tracker updated daily. Let's get you to NY! 💪🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120104,"output":88,"cacheRead":23670,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143862,"cost":{"input":0.0360312,"output":0.00010559999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0014202,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03755699999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775796045644,"responseId":"0627b24da34ddaba20111c949f9c789c"}}
