{"type":"message","id":"e6e6d47c","parentId":"6d723aa8","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.057Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-04-10 00:40:08 EDT] Exec completed (tender-c, code 0) :: \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\" }, \"delivery\": { \"mode\": \"announce\", \"channel\": \"telegram\", \"to\": \"8212808444\" }, \"state\": { \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775876400000 } } [plugins] [lcm…\nSystem (untrusted): [2026-04-10 00:40:45 EDT] Exec completed (plaid-pi, code 0) :: ssage to Telegram chat 8212808444 and nothing else: 'Bobby — end of day check! 💪 Drop your DD earnings and any spending you had today so I can update your gap tracker and keep yo…\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"491\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 00:41 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nwe can always adjust the goal for may and june correct? like what would happen if i make 164 every day for the rest until i move hypothetically?"}],"timestamp":1775796091446}}
{"type":"message","id":"36238a4f","parentId":"e6e6d47c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.057Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is asking about adjusting the goal for May and June. Let me think about this:\n\nIf he makes $164/day from now until he moves (let's say end of April = 21 days, May = 31 days, June = 30 days = about 82 days total from Apr 10 onwards):\n\n$164 × 82 = $13,448 extra earned\n\nBut he only needs to close a $612 gap. So if he hits $164/day consistently, he'd be way ahead.\n\nThe real question is: what does he NEED for the move? The calendar shows him ending at $6,277.79 by June 10. But that was with $125/day, not $164/day.\n \nSo the difference is significant—hitting $164/day versus the planned $125/day through June 10 would actually put him about $3,198 ahead of the current projection. That's substantial cushion for the move. But I should clarify what his actual goal is before we lock in the numbers.","thinkingSignature":"7356998fe2578df0b88eb715547b0bdeb94e10f013a67945de68a688cf690efc"},{"type":"text","text":"Yes — we can always adjust!\n\n**$164/day through end of April** (21 days) = closes the $612 gap\n\n**If you kept $164/day through May and June:**\n- Extra earned above $125/day: +$39/day\n- Apr 10-30: +$819\n- May (31 days): +$1,209\n- June 1-10: +$390\n- **Total extra above plan: +$2,418**\n\nThat would put you at $6,277 + $2,418 = **~$8,695 by June 10**\n\nvs the calendar's $6,277\n\nWay more cushion for the move!\n\nBut here's the thing: we can adjust as you go. April first — let's see if $164/day is even realistic for you. If it is, we extend it. If not, we adjust.\n\nOne day at a time Bobby. Let's start tomorrow. 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98,"output":405,"cacheRead":141779,"cacheWrite":1918,"totalTokens":144200,"cost":{"input":0.0000294,"output":0.000486,"cacheRead":0.008506739999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00071925000000