{"type":"message","id":"f2b85261","parentId":"5cf4c752","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.058Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"493\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 00:42 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nokay im just really stressed"}],"timestamp":1775796134976}}
{"type":"message","id":"837b201f","parentId":"f2b85261","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is stressed. He just shared something vulnerable. I should acknowledge that, be supportive, and reassure him.","thinkingSignature":"2f74d81b46381668091a26e9743fc891eb010632c2ee7f4bce822bad1bcdde46"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] I hear you Bobby. Money stress is real — especially when you're trying to make a big move and everything feels like it's adding up.\n\nBut here's what I want you to hear:\n\nYou're DOING the work. You're grinding DD every day. You're tracking. You're paying bills on time. You're having hard conversations with yourself about goals.\n\nThat's more than most people do.\n\nTomorrow is a new day. One day at a time. You don't have to figure out May and June right now — just tomorrow.\n\nGo get some sleep. I'll be here in the morning and we'll start fresh. You've got this. 💪🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98,"output":158,"cacheRead":143769,"cacheWrite":242,"totalTokens":144267,"cost":{"input":0.0000294,"output":0.0001896,"cacheRead":0.00862614,"cacheWrite":0.00009075,"total":0.00893589}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775796134982,"responseId":"0627b2a7ed318667fd91f7829df8a6b4"}}
