{"type":"message","id":"5af9ad4a","parentId":"f15129ba","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.058Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"495\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 00:42 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nalso tomorrow i really dont know if ill be able to dash beucase of the hockey game and i have to get my oil changed before i even drive another shift for DD beucase its a lot on my car especially with the oil change due"}],"timestamp":1775796173500}}
{"type":"message","id":"a3bc58e1","parentId":"5af9ad4a","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is saying he might not be able to DD tomorrow because of the hockey game AND he needs to get his oil changed first. These are both valid things - he needs to get his oil changed before he drives more for DD (smart to maintain the car), and he has the hockey game which is taking up time.\n\nSo tomorrow (April 10) he might not earn much from DD. Let me acknowledge this and note that we need to track what he CAN earn tomorrow.","thinkingSignature":"840c13bc1ebe171608e17fe0e9e93b93046d4d1e707003d0056c64402ffac9b4"},{"type":"text","text":"That's fine Bobby — don't stress about tomorrow. \n\nHockey game = time away from DD\nOil change = needs to happen before more driving\n\nSo tomorrow might be a low-DD day. That's okay. We just need to know:\n- How much DD did you earn (if any)?\n- How much was the oil change?\n\nWe'll work with the real numbers. No guilt, no shame — just track what happens and keep moving forward.\n\nGo enjoy the hockey game! 🎉 And get that oil changed. Car maintenance is part of the DD business. \n\nWe pick back up after tomorrow with real numbers. 💪🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98,"output":229,"cacheRead":144107,"cacheWrite":198,"totalTokens":144632,"cost":{"input":0.0000294,"output":0.0002748,"cacheRead":0.008646419999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00007425,"total":0.009024869999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775796173505,"responseId":"0627b2cd06984317e1a8922c41557807"}}
