{"type":"message","id":"c186812e","parentId":"1e890b20","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.062Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is feeling stressed and defeated. He's saying it will take a miracle to catch up. I need to be encouraging but realistic. Let me reframe this for him.He has:\n- $1,232.71 cash\n- Bills remaining: ~$888\n- After bills: ~$345 cushion\n\nPlus DD income daily. It's tight but not impossible. He's been through this before - the 2 missed days, the shortfalls, the bills adding up. He needs encouragement, not me running more numbers at him right now.","thinkingSignature":"c3c453052be18dfc60927b82a0b852e063d2b28044c22838deca665ddafd88f4"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey — stop.\n\nYou've been through worse than this and you're still here. Still fighting.\n\n$1,232 in cash. Bills are being paid. Car is fixed. You're DDing tonight.\n\nIt's not a miracle — it's one day at a time. One dollar at a time.\n\nYou don't have to see the whole mountain from the bottom. You just have to take the next step.\n\nGo get 'em tonight. We'll figure out tomorrow when tomorrow comes. 💪🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98,"output":211,"cacheRead":153375,"cacheWrite":433,"totalTokens":154117,"cost":{"input":0.0000294,"output":0.0002532,"cacheRead":0.009202499999999999,"cacheWrite":0.000162375,"total":0.009647474999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775859040840,"responseId":"0628a861b0125e7f79fe89e45a0edd06"}}
