{"type":"message","id":"34ac6143","parentId":"33862d1d","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.063Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is asking about T-Mobile again and what bills are coming up. Let me confirm that yes, he paid the T-Mobile bill ($196.59) and give him the upcoming bills list.\n\nLooking at his April bills tracker:\n- April 10: T-Mobile (phone bill) $196.59 - ✅ PAID Apr 10\n- April 11: Affirm - Affirm Virtual Card - $25.74\n- April 12: Affirm - Affirm Virtual Card - $29.87\n- April 15: Capital One Platinum Card - $25.00\n- April 15: Discover Card - $25.00\n- April 15: GEICO Insurance - $187.25\n- April 17: Affirm - T-Mobile - $15.31\n- April 21: Affirm - T-Mobile - $18.00\n- April 27: Affirm - Broadwaydirect.com - $13.41\n- April 27: Capital One Quicksilver - $411.00\n- April 28: Chase - $74.00\n- April 30: Apple Card Payment - $64.00\n\nLet me give him the upcoming bills.","thinkingSignature":"49c8b8af23065f3c2b41deca6af026ec3bb574a1633309c17f4717807fefc974"},{"type":"text","text":"Yes you paid the $196.59 T-Mobile bill — ✅ DONE!\n\n**Upcoming bills:**\n\n| Date | Bill | Amount |\n|------|------|--------|\n| Apr 11 | Affirm - Affirm Virtual Card | $25.74 |\n| Apr 12 | Affirm - Affirm Virtual Card | $29.87 |\n| Apr 15 | Cap One + Discover + GEICO | $237.25 |\n| Apr 17 | Affirm - T-Mobile | $15.31 |\n| Apr 21 | Affirm - T-Mobile | $18.00 |\n| Apr 27 | Affirm + Cap One Quicksilver | $424.41 |\n| Apr 28 | Chase | $74.00 |\n| Apr 30 | Apple Card | $64.00 |\n\n**Total coming up: $888.58**\n\nBig ones are Apr 15 ($237.25) and Apr 27 ($424.41). 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98,"output":447,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":154172,"totalTokens":154717,"cost":{"input":0.0000294,"output":0.0005364,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.057814500000000005,"total":0.0583803}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775867822708,"responseId":"0628caafe7c1eb81ba7564366e8fcae5"}}
