{"type":"message","id":"1a923723","parentId":"0661049a","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is asking for a simple breakdown of remaining bills for April. Let me get the exact numbers.\n\nUpcoming bills (not paid yet):\n- Apr 11: Affirm Virtual Card - $25.74\n- Apr 12: Affirm Virtual Card - $29.87\n- Apr 15: Cap One Platinum - $25.00\n- Apr 15: Discover Card - $25.00\n- Apr 15: GEICO Insurance - $187.25\n- Apr 17: Affirm T-Mobile - $15.31\n- Apr 21: Affirm T-Mobile - $18.00\n- Apr 27: Affirm Broadwaydirect - $13.41\n- Apr 27: Capital One Quicksilver - $411.00\n- Apr 28: Chase - $74.00\n- Apr 30: Apple Card Payment - $64.00\n\nTotal: $25.74 + $29.87 + $25 + $25 + $187.25 + $15.31 + $18 + $13.41 + $411 + $74 + $64 = $888.58\n","thinkingSignature":"42380c56938212856cba0536ec9326c12d59508828489fd45e76be36ad72fcb3"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**Remaining bills for April:**\n\n| Date | Bill | Amount |\n|------|------|--------|\n| Apr 11 | Affirm Virtual Card | $25.74 |\n| Apr 12 | Affirm Virtual Card | $29.87 |\n| Apr 15 | Cap One Platinum | $25.00 |\n| Apr 15 | Discover Card | $25.00 |\n| Apr 15 | GEICO Insurance | $187.25 |\n| Apr 17 | Affirm T-Mobile | $15.31 |\n| Apr 21 | Affirm T-Mobile | $18.00 |\n| Apr 27 | Affirm Broadwaydirect | $13.41 |\n| Apr 27 | Capital One Quicksilver | $411.00 |\n| Apr 28 | Chase | $74.00 |\n| Apr 30 | Apple Card | $64.00 |\n\n**Total: $888.58**\n\nThat's what you owe for the rest of April. 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":154434,"output":437,"cacheRead":1184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":156055,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775881836593,"responseId":"0629016ca427fe22480641b2a8a2a165"}}
