{"type":"message","id":"57fb1e0e","parentId":"d915fcb8","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.069Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great! April 27 Affirm Broadwaydirect.com marked as PAID.\n","thinkingSignature":"864b903ee3db5a7031680350b22ee7984fb4548ab16f59b688b194c3a00406b9"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nDone! Broadwaydirect ✅ PAID Apr 12!\n\n**Only 2 bills left for April:**\n- Apr 27: $411.00 (Cap One Quicksilver)\n- Apr 28: $74.00 (Chase)\n- Apr 30: $64.00 (Apple Card)\n\n**Total remaining: $549.00** — and the big one ($411) is Apr 27.\n\nYou've paid off so much tonight Bobby! Huge win! 💪🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":174,"output":120,"cacheRead":160896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":161190,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775967864061,"responseId":"062a517888b247c8a5995d4f54af9758"}}
