{"type":"message","id":"409c6d0d","parentId":"867239b5","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.074Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is asking what happens if he sustains $200/day from now until the move (June 10).\n\nLet me calculate:\n- Today is April 12, June 10 is 59 days away (April 13-30 = 18 days, May = 31 days, June 1-10 = 10 days, Total = 59 days)\n\n$200/day × 59 days = $11,800 earned\n\nExtra above $125/day = $75/day × 59 = $4,425 extra\n\nOriginal calendar: $6,277 by June 10\n\nIf he does $200/day:\n- Extra earned above $125: $4,425\n- Gap to close from now: ~$1,098\n- Net extra after closing gap: $4,425 - $1,098 = $3,327 ahead\n\nStarting cash $1,134 + $11,800 - $549 in remaining April bills = ~$12,385 by June 10\n\nvs original $6,277 projection\n\nThat's HUGE! He'd have double what the calendar projected!\n\nActually let me be more precise. He has 18 days left in April at $200/day = $3,600\nThen 31 days in May = $6,200\nThen 10 days in June = $2,000\nTotal: $11,800 over 59 days\n\nExtra above $125: $75 × 59 = $4,425\n\nStarting gap: ~$1,098\n\nHe'd be $3,327 ahead of where the calendar says he'd be by June 10.\n\n$1,134 + $11,800 - $549 (April remaining bills) = $12,385 by June 10\n\nThat's incredible!","thinkingSignature":"6e0ed7637b64bfa18df41b764b5357fe0b16cba471519700aa5d8a1172736e1b"},{"type":"text","text":"Bobby — let me run this:\n\n**April 12 to June 10 = 59 days**\n\n**$200/day × 59 days = $11,800 earned**\n\n**Extra above $125/day = $75/day × 59 = $4,425 extra**\n\n**Original calendar: $6,277 by June 10**\n\n**Your projection at $200/day:**\n- $1,134 (current) + $11,800 - $549 (April bills) = **$12,385 by June 10**\n\n**vs calendar $6,277**\n\n**$6,108 MORE than the calendar projected!**\n\nYou'd have DOUBLE what the calendar thought you would by June 10.\n\nThat's enough for:\n- Luckey Platt deposit: $2,900\n- Jackman Drive deposit: $3,700\n- LEFT OVER: ~$5,785\n\nBobby — $200/day is a GAME CHANGER. That's what closes the gap AND funds the move in a big way.\n\nIs that realistic for you? 💪🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":575,"cacheRead":168411,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":168986,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776044945383,"responseId":"062b7e916395b51a18bb817cd97db261"}}
