{"type":"message","id":"f2c5cd40","parentId":"d949831e","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby made $114.25 today. That's short of the $164 goal and way short of the $200 goal he wanted. But he got a late start, so that's understandable.","thinkingSignature":"beb2545cfbb4625df3628945a2b268395b537922c9327ccfe46edb1be6c7ec0b"},{"type":"text","text":"$114.25 is still $114 in your pocket! Late start happens Bobby.\n\n**$114.25 / $200 = 57%** of the new $200 goal\n\n$85.75 short of $200 today. Some days you'll make more, some days less.\n\nTomorrow is a new day. No apologies needed — we work with what you got! 💪🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98,"output":122,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":169319,"totalTokens":169539,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776129954315,"responseId":"062ccaa22b43c429833a4bbb02ddb78a"}}
