{"type":"message","id":"28bb14bb","parentId":"d9ddc63a","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Dean wants me to send Bobby a full April bills breakdown. Let me pull it from the April_Bills.md file and give the complete picture.\n","thinkingSignature":"bc43b4583a493b36cce9d75b7c628cff870e3a260f3067d8496743136861b078"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**Full April Bills Breakdown:**\n\n| Due Date | Bill | Amount | Status |\n|----------|------|--------|--------|\n| Apr 1 | Xfinity Internet | $118.00 | ✅ PAID |\n| Apr 2 | Affirm - Marriott Hotels | $129.59 | ✅ PAID |\n| Apr 3 | KUB (old apartment) | $362.20 | ✅ PAID |\n| Apr 8 | T-Mobile (2 of 2) | $98.30 | ✅ PAID |\n| Apr 9 | Affirm - Hilton Hotels | $23.50 | ✅ PAID |\n| Apr 10 | T-Mobile (phone bill) | $196.59 | ✅ PAID |\n| Apr 11 | Affirm - Affirm Virtual Card | $25.74 | ✅ PAID |\n| Apr 12 | Affirm - Affirm Virtual Card | $29.87 | ✅ PAID |\n| Apr 15 | Capital One Platinum Card | $25.00 | ✅ PAID Apr 12 |\n| Apr 15 | Discover Card | $25.00 | ✅ PAID Apr 12 |\n| Apr 15 | GEICO Insurance | $187.25 | ✅ PAID Apr 12 |\n| Apr 17 | Affirm - T-Mobile | $15.31 | ✅ PAID Apr 12 |\n| Apr 21 | Affirm - T-Mobile | $18.00 | ✅ PAID Apr 12 |\n| Apr 27 | Affirm - Broadwaydirect.com | $13.41 | ✅ PAID Apr 12 |\n| Apr 27 | Capital One Quicksilver | $411.00 | $150 PAID → **$261 owed** |\n| Apr 28 | Chase | $74.00 | ✅ PAID ($80) |\n| Apr 30 | Apple Card Payment | $64.00 | ✅ PAID Apr 14 |\n\n**Summary:**\n- Total bills this month: ~$1,792\n- Paid: ~$1,331\n- Remaining owed: **$261** (just Cap One Quicksilver left!)\n\n🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":139052,"output":469,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139777,"cost":{"input":0.0417156,"output":0.0005628,"cacheRead":0.00001536,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04229376}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776308389930,"responseId":"062f83a6298be377a97f0c0e46d728