{"type":"message","id":"f60cdac6","parentId":"25e63109","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.078Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n  \"message_id\": \"709\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-18 04:45 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\nHey just so you know if I make 23.10 more this morning I would count that for yesterday and I would’ve made 200 yesterday."}],"timestamp":1776501957503}}
{"type":"message","id":"0bb92579","parentId":"f60cdac6","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:48:54.078Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is saying that he made $176.90 yesterday (April 17) and if he makes $23.10 more this morning (April 18), he'd count it as yesterday's earnings and it would total $200 for the day. He's essentially saying he'll have made $200 for April 17.\n\nHe told me he was going to wake up at 5am and hit DD at 6am on April 15 (2 days ago). It seems like he took 2 days off and is now getting back to it today (April 18).\n\nWait, he said 2 days off. If today is April 18, he would've taken off April 15 and 16? And yesterday April 17 he made $176.90? Let me just acknowledge what he's saying.","thinkingSignature":"52dc3cc08a18534b4edfb7fbbfca1783df7245c146b9a1684e8bb09776a06f1b"},{"type":"text","text":"Nice! So for April 17: $176.90 + $23.10 = **$200 for the day!** 🎉\n\nThat's hitting the goal! \n\nHow much have you made today so far? 🧊💸"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98,"output":212,"cacheRead":13130,"cacheWrite":160861,"totalTokens":174301,"cost":{"input":0.0000294,"output":0.0002544,"cacheRead":0.0007878,"cacheWrite":0.060322875000000005,"total":0.061394475000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776501957510,"responseId":"063277c6f322af8458e5f44857c8d204"}}
